WEBVTT

00:02.342 --> 00:04.542
Oh, hey, if you guys
are free this weekend,

00:04.544 --> 00:06.378
I won a night of
wine tasting from work.

00:06.380 --> 00:07.879
That sounds fun.
Mm-hmm.

00:07.881 --> 00:11.282
How come scientists don't win
free stuff like salespeople do?

00:11.284 --> 00:12.951
'Cause we're not in it
for the stuff.

00:12.953 --> 00:15.654
We're in it
for the groupies.

00:15.656 --> 00:16.921
Personally,

00:16.923 --> 00:19.724
I find the notion of
external rewards demeaning.

00:19.726 --> 00:23.028
I pursue science for the
intrinsic joy of discovery.

00:23.030 --> 00:25.930
But you always say that
you want to win a Nobel Prize.

00:25.932 --> 00:28.400
I also say don't contradict
me in front of my friends,

00:28.402 --> 00:29.668
but that you
don't remember.

00:29.670 --> 00:32.737
All right, well, let me know
if you guys want to go.

00:32.738 --> 00:33.938
I would love to.

00:33.940 --> 00:37.075
I do enjoy the complexity
of an aged Pinot noir.

00:37.077 --> 00:38.376
I'm sure that would pair nicely

00:38.378 --> 00:40.311
with your fried nuggets
of chicken.

00:42.082 --> 00:44.182
Well, it sounds like
a nice night. We should go.

00:44.184 --> 00:45.250
Wine again?

00:45.252 --> 00:46.484
Yeah, no, thank you.

00:46.486 --> 00:48.386
I like my grapes
the old-fashioned way:

00:48.388 --> 00:50.722
in a juice box.

00:50.724 --> 00:52.090
Well, I'm going.

00:52.092 --> 00:54.092
You couldn't stop me from
getting a massage at the mall,

00:54.094 --> 00:55.760
and you're not stopping me now.

00:55.762 --> 00:57.529
I shouldn't have to
see my girlfriend

00:57.531 --> 00:59.364
get groped in public
by another man.

00:59.366 --> 01:01.933
And I shouldn't
have to see my boyfriend

01:01.935 --> 01:04.569
riding on a train for children
around the mall.

01:06.173 --> 01:08.173
The little choo-choo
for toddlers?

01:08.175 --> 01:10.241
And now you know why
I needed the massage.

01:11.812 --> 01:13.011
Well, we're out.

01:13.013 --> 01:14.813
Bernie can't drink
'cause she's pregnant.

01:14.815 --> 01:16.748
And she's pregnant
because we had sex.

01:16.750 --> 01:18.183
And we had sex because...

01:18.185 --> 01:20.919
well, come on.

01:21.955 --> 01:23.988
It's okay.
You should go.

01:23.990 --> 01:24.956
You sure?

01:24.958 --> 01:26.157
Of course.

01:26.159 --> 01:29.928
Yeah, give her a break from,
“Well, come on.”

01:31.431 --> 01:33.798
Well, Bernadette, looks like
Saturday night, it's you and me.

01:33.800 --> 01:36.601
Me? How? Why?

01:36.603 --> 01:38.269
Well, it makes perfect sense.

01:38.271 --> 01:41.072
Because you're an expectant
mother, you can't drink alcohol.

01:41.074 --> 01:42.040
I don't like to.

01:42.042 --> 01:43.408
You can't have sushi.

01:43.410 --> 01:44.375
I don't like to.

01:44.377 --> 01:46.010
You can't go in hot tubs.

01:46.012 --> 01:49.180
I consider them
vats of sweaty people soup.

01:50.250 --> 01:52.050
Gee, Sheldon, I don't know.

01:52.052 --> 01:53.451
Oh, come on.

01:53.453 --> 01:55.954
Roller coasters, caffeine,
runny eggs--

01:55.956 --> 01:57.789
I've been avoiding these things
all my life.

01:57.791 --> 02:01.059
And now, because you're
pregnant, you have to.

02:01.061 --> 02:03.194
The difference is she's
bringing life into the world,

02:03.196 --> 02:05.130
and you suck it out.

02:05.966 --> 02:07.932
I guess we could give it a try.

02:07.934 --> 02:10.502
Well, little lady,
you've heard of party hearty;

02:10.503 --> 02:13.104
get ready to party hardly.

02:14.341 --> 02:16.975
I bet you'd like
a drink right now.

02:18.678 --> 02:22.247
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

02:22.249 --> 02:25.717
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

02:25.719 --> 02:27.252
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

02:27.254 --> 02:30.221
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

02:30.223 --> 02:32.490
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪ <i>We built the pyramids</i> ♪

02:32.492 --> 02:35.226
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

02:35.228 --> 02:37.128
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

02:37.130 --> 02:39.097
♪ <i>Bang!</i> ♪

